'''Hespérides Trough''' ({{coord|60|21|S|50|50|W|source:GNIS|display=inline,title}}) is an [[Trough (geology)|undersea trough]] named for the Spanish research vessel ''Hespérides''. The name was approved by the [[Advisory Committee on Undersea Features]] in November 1995.<ref name=gnis/>

