This is a list of Governors for [[Stockholm County]] of [[Sweden]]. Stockholm County separated from [[Uppland County]], the first time from 1641 to 1654, and then finally in 1719. The [[Cities of Sweden|City]] of [[Stockholm]] was separately governed by the [[Over-Governor of Stockholm]] until 1967, when it was integrated into Stockholm County. The governors reside in [[Tessin Palace]].
==Governors==
